Package labb5.simulation.general

Class Event

java.lang.Object
labb5.simulation.general.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Event>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrivalEvent, ClosingEvent, PayLeaveEvent, ShoppingEvent, StartEvent, StopEvent
public abstract class Event extends Object implements Comparable<Event>
The abstract base class for all general state contexts. The absolute time from the simulation start when the event should occur is stored in this class, along with methods for run, getTime and compareTo that compares the time it should occur with the current Time.
Author:
Dino Lolic, Stefan Jonsson, William Kiwanuka, Arvid From
